==English==

===Noun Phrase===
{{Wikipedia}}
'''blue screen of death'''

#''Computing.'' The screen displayed by [[Microsoft]]'s [[Windows]] [[operating system]] when it cannot (or is in danger of being unable to) recover from a system error.  Abbreviation: [[BSOD]].

